OL,3,CBiker jailed after dangerous overtake
OL,4,Cattempt led to another rider losing a
OL,5,Cleg
OL,7,FThe 52-year-old pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving and was jailed for 20 months.
OL,11,FGoff overtook an RAC recovery van that
OL,12,Fwas towing her partner's vehicle. The
OL,13,Fdangerous manoeuvre placed her
OL,14,FKawasaki motorcycle directly into the
OL,15,Fpath of an oncoming Honda bike.
OL,17,FDevon and Cornwall Police said the
OL,18,Fconditions on the road at the time of
OL,19,Fthe crash were "darkening, wet and
OL,20,Ffoggy".
