OL,3,CBiker jailed after dangerous overtake
OL,4,Cattempt led to another rider losing a
OL,5,Cleg
OL,7,FDetective Constable Alan Kennedy from
OL,8,Fthe Serious Collisions Investigation
OL,9,FTeam told the court: "This was a
OL,10,Ftotally avoidable collision.
OL,12,F"Goff's riding fell far below the
OL,13,Fstandard expected of a road user, and
OL,14,Fthe decision to perform the overtake
OL,15,Fwas made even worse by the poor
OL,16,Fweather conditions at the time."
OL,18,FThe Honda rider, who has not been
OL,19,Fnamed, suffered catastrophic injuries,
OL,20,Fincluding the amputation of one leg.
