OL,7,FBoth motorcycles were extensively
OL,8,Fdamaged, and the RAC van also
OL,9,Fsustained bodywork damage to the
OL,10,Fdriver's door.
OL,12,FEvidence presented in court included
OL,13,Fhelmet camera footage from Goff, which
OL,14,Fprosecutors said revealed "numerous
OL,15,Fbreaches of the Highway Code"
OL,16,Fthroughout the day and "an extended
OL,17,Fperiod of poor riding in adverse
OL,18,Fconditions" immediately before the
OL,19,Fcrash.
