OL,7,FIn addition to the prison sentence,
OL,8,FJudge Martin Stephens QC disqualified
OL,9,FGoff from driving for four years.
OL,11,FSpeaking after the sentencing, DC
OL,12,FKennedy added: "We hope this case will
OL,13,Fserve as a reminder that every
OL,14,Fmanoeuvre can have tragic consequences.
OL,16,F"Goff's actions on that day resulted
OL,17,Fin an injury which has changed the
OL,18,Flife of another motorcycle rider
OL,19,Fforever."
